      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should ask them but i can't get an appointment for like two weeks and im literally exhausted. it's just melatonin right? like it's just a natural supplement. it doesn't seem like it would interact badly with a sleep pill since they both just help you drift off. i'm just looking for a quick way to get through tonight without feeling like a zombie.",
